    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like there's a lot of hidden stuff in there that isn't explicitly spelled out. like, what if something small goes wrong that i didn't even realize was a \"breach\"? could they use this clause to come after me for something tiny just to be difficult? is there a way to phrase it so they can't just jump on every little mistake?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
